{"html": [{"t": "<div><div class=\"p\">&#xA0;</div></div>", "i": 8437501}, {"t": "<div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  Por resoluci&#xF3;n N&#xBA; 1.625, de 25 de junio de 2008, de esta Subsecretar&#xED;a, autor&#xED;zase a JAVIER FERNANDO ALVARADO VIDAL para instalar, por el per&#xED;odo de seis meses contados desde el 1&#xBA; de octubre de 2008, colectores de semillas de chorito (Mythilus chilensis) en 3 sectores al norte de Punta Dequio, Estero de Castro, X Regi&#xF3;n, cuyas superficies y coordenadas geogr&#xE1;ficas, referidas a la carta SHOA N&#xBA; 7370 Datum WGS-84, son las siguientes:</div><br><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  Sector 1: 2,80 hect&#xE1;reas</div><br><div class=\"p\">&nbsp;  V&#xE9;rtice&nbsp;  Latitud (S)&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Longitud (W)</div><br><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  A&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 42&#xB0;29&apos;44,47&quot;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 73&#xB0;44&apos;50,96&quot;</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  B&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 42&#xB0;29&apos;44,42&quot;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 73&#xB0;44&apos;45,98&quot;</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  C&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 42&#xB0;29&apos;52,35&quot;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 73&#xB0;44&apos;50,31&quot;</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  D&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 42&#xB0;29&apos;52,35&quot;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 73&#xB0;44&apos;55,44&quot;</div><br><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  Sector 2: 3,01 hect&#xE1;reas</div><br><div class=\"p\">&nbsp;  V&#xE9;rtice&nbsp; Latitud (S)&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  Longitud (W)</div><br><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  A&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 42&#xB0;30&apos;01,80&quot;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 73&#xB0;45&apos;00,78&quot;</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  B&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 42&#xB0;30&apos;01,74&quot;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 73&#xB0;44&apos;55,39&quot;</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  C&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 42&#xB0;30&apos;09,70&quot;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 73&#xB0;44&apos;59,84&quot;</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  D&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 42&#xB0;30&apos;09,70&quot;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;